# simple-fb2-reader
Simple tool to read FB2 books. Developed using GTK+3.
=====================================================

Features ("-" - not supported yet, "~" - partial support):
- supports fb2, fb2.zip and txt files
- saving reading position
- saving window state, size and position
- search text in book
- URI(with backward button and tooltips)
- full 2.1 format support(-stylesheet, ~table)
- navigation
- russian and english gui
- user themes(see ~/.config/simple-fb2-reader/config.cfg)


Depends:
- libxml2		>= 2.8.0
- libgtk-3-0		>= 3.4.2
- libglib		>= 2.33.12
- libzip2		>= 0.10.1


Build Depends:
- debhelper		>= 8.0.0
- libxml2-dev		>= 2.8.0
- libgtk-3-dev		>= 3.4.2
- libglib2.0-dev	>= 2.32.4
- libzip-dev		>= 0.10.1
- pkg-config		>= 0.26
- libc-dev-bin		>= 2.13
- gettext		>= 0.18.1.1
